foreign_films.title: Foreign Films
foreign_films.description: From Asia to Europe and beyond - Expand your cinematic horizons with our top picks from across the globe.

287458.title: Ghidorah, the Three-Headed Monster
287458.description: After a meteorite unleashes a three-headed beast upon Tokyo, Mothra tries to unite with Godzilla and Rodan to battle the extraterrestrial threat.

301339.title: Ju-On: The Grudge 2
301339.description: When a social worker enters a home where a family was once brutally killed, an evil spirit is awakened and triggers a terrifying chain of events.

314139.title: Cannibal
314139.description: A serial killer who dines on the women he murders begins to question everything when a woman awakens a kind of love he had long since given up on.

314149.title: Puppylove
314149.description: When a free-spirited girl befriends a young teenager, they leave childhood behind to embrace a dangerous world of clubbing and sex with strange men.

314511.title: 22 Bullets
314511.description: Having been left for dead with 22 bullets in his body after being shot by a former childhood friend, a retired mobster sets out to get his revenge.

378839.title: Dismay
378839.description: A farmer incites a rebellion from his two sons when he installs his young mistress as the new woman of the house immediately after his wife's death.

409164.title: Baby Boss
409164.description: In childhood, Tang Miao's parents mysteriously disappeared and she was living in the orphanage, longing for a Prince charming from the sky. Xiao Yishu was undoubtedly this person, handsome and wealthy. With the help of this man, Tang not only successfully completed her studies, but also harvested an unforgettable love. But an explosion occurred in Xiao's Family building. Xiao and the board members of his company were all contaminated with radioactive contamination and all became the body of the 10-year-old child. The fate of the family, the love between Tang and Xiao, let's see what will happen...

417676.title: Madrid, 1987
417676.description: Inside four walls—two characters: old and young, teacher and pupil, man and woman—conjure rationalism, explore politics and discover one another.

448257.title: Amores Perros
448257.description: A horrific car accident connects the lives of three strangers: a lovesick dog fighter, an injured supermodel and a hitman running from his past.

451921.title: Special Forces
451921.description: When a war correspondent is taken hostage by the Taliban, a group of soldiers risk their lives in a relentless pursuit to bring her home.

453783.title: Bang Gang
453783.description: When a suburban teen falls for a boy within her circle of friends, she tries to impress him by initiating a game that pushes their sexual boundaries.

457296.title: Hide and Seek
457296.description: An obsessive-compulsive father discovers his brother has gone missing. Then terror and paranoia invade his own home, pushing his family to the brink.

465170.title: Goodnight Mommy
465170.description: Young twin brothers vow to protect each other when their mother comes home with her face obscured by bandages, which makes them question her identity.

465636.title: The End?
465636.description: When a young businessman gets locked in his office elevator, he discovers a deadly virus that has begun to infect and transform people into zombies.

466725.title: Sennentuntschi
466725.description: A mysterious woman appears in an Alpine village, stirring suspicion that she's a murderous demon or the terrifying embodiment of a local legend.

467545.title: The Grandmaster
467545.description: The extraordinary life of a martial arts master unfolds across decades in China. His triumphs and struggles cement him as a real-life legend.

475177.title: All Things Fair
475177.description: A forbidden relationship between a teen student and his adult, female teacher in World War II-era Sweden has consequences neither of them expect.

475822.title: Departures
475822.description: Foreign Language Oscar-winner about a recently unemployed cellist musician who ends up taking a job preparing the dead for their funerals.

489178.description: In 1944, manslaughter between nationalities occur when Estonians of the withdrawing German forces fight Estonian recruits in the Soviet Red Army.

490092.title: Viking
490092.description: In the 10th century, after the death of his father, a viking prince is forced into exile, and must escape the grasp of his dangerous brother.

492083.title: You Will Be Mine
492083.description: A gifted pianist is seduced by her female roommate, setting off a romance that may overwhelm her identity as she falls under her sadistic control.

499293.title: Ong Bak 3: The Final Battle
499293.description: Picking up where the saga left off, Tien, who was captured and beaten, returns to the Kana Khone village, to learn new skills and face a final duel.

506145.title: The Wailing
506145.description: A policeman races against time to save his daughter from a mysterious sickness spreading through a small village.

507995.title: Among Adults
507995.description: Twelve adults: six women and six men attempt to navigate love, lies, betrayal and manipulation inside each of their personal relationships.

512689.title: Little Forest
512689.description: When a wayward young woman finally has her fill of city life, she returns to her countryside roots and finally finds what she’s always been searching for.

513365.title: Seoul Station
513365.description: When a sudden zombie pandemic unleashes its horrors in downtown Seoul, several groups of city-dwellers do what they must to try and survive.

513857.title: No Excuses
513857.description: What if women were allowed to compete in a traditionally male dominated crossfit gym? This doc takes on gender equality in the fitness world.

518180.title: Django (Dubbed)
518180.description: A mysterious loner who enters a ghost town on the US-Mexico border dragging a coffin behind him saves a prostitute and gets enmeshed in a savage feud.

519901.title: All About Lily Chou-Chou
519901.description: A haunting look at teens in Japan whose lives go in different, and sometimes disturbing, directions as they find meaning in a musician’s songs.

521907.title: Monkey King 2
521907.description: It’s up to the brave Monkey King to escort a monk away from a wasteland as he attempts to retrieve sacred scriptures, which will stop a demon.

523582.title: Valentine: The Dark Avenger
523582.description: A cafe waitress who dreams of acting is recruited by men she believes to be filmmakers, but who transform her into a real masked anti-crime heroine.

525892.title: Golden Temple Amazons
525892.description: Raised by the Amazon tribe that killed her parents, a woman discovers her true origin and vows revenge on the warrior huntresses who held her captive.

526431.title: Down by Love
526431.description: Inspired by true events in 2011, the married warden of a Versailles prison and a female inmate set off a national firestorm when they fall in love.

526969.title: Terra Formars
526969.description: When 21st-century scientists seed Mars with algae and roaches to help the toxic atmosphere, a mission flight there disappears and a new ship must go.

531685.title: The Girl Who Kicked the Hornet's Nest
531685.description: The third and final installment of Stieg Larsson's "Millennium" series finds hacker Lisbeth Salander fighting for her life in an ICU.

546235.title: Squadron 303: The Battle of Britain
546235.description: The true story of pilots who escape occupied Poland and join an elite,heroic squad defending England from the Nazi Luftwaffe in the Battle of Britain.

548642.title: Kiss Me
548642.description: Two women in their 30s feel an instant attraction upon meeting at their parents’ engagement party, realizing they will be stepsisters, and maybe more.

548907.title: Paris 05:59: Théo & Hugo
548907.description: Near midnight in a gay sex club, two men share unbridled desire, which by morning, as they wander the streets of Paris, becomes a tender love affair.

554108.title: Offside
554108.description: Follow the commitment, passion and comradery of a female Polish football team and their coach during their grueling pre-season training.

557482.title: One Missed Call
557482.description: A student receives a phone message from her future self, ending with her own death scream.

560873.title: Ip Man: The Final Fight (Dubbed)
560873.description: In postwar Hong Kong, a real-life Wing Chun grandmaster rises to action once more, as kung fu rivals draw him into a dark, dangerous underworld.

560875.title: Special ID (Dubbed)
560875.description: An undercover cop infiltrates a ruthless crime syndicate and risks everything to shield his life and family, after the boss vows to kill all traitors.

562130.title: GonJiam: Haunted Asylum
562130.description: The film crew of an online horror series gets far more footage than they bargained for when they shoot an episode in an abandoned asylum.

562275.title: House of Sleeping Beauties
562275.description: An older man’s grief over his wife’s tragic death causes him to visit a bizarre brothel where the workers are drugged, and a shocking twist awaits.

562835.title: Uncaged
562835.description: A zoo veterinarian is caught up in a grisly adventure as she leads the hunt for a monstrous lion terrorizing the Dutch capital of Amsterdam

562860.title: Vlad the Impaler
562860.description: In 15th century Turkey, seven fearless heroes build up to fight the cruel and ruthless Vlad The Impaler, to end his rule once and for all.

565878.title: Redbad
565878.description: In 700 AD, as epic battles rage for control of Europe, the legend of pagan warrior king is born, as is a new weapon against his people: Christianity.

566803.title: A Man Called Ove
566803.description: When a boisterous Persian family, including a pregnant woman, moves next door to the neighborhood’s grumpy old man, unexpected love and kinship bloom.

568421.title: Beauty and the Beast
568421.description: Award-winning version of the fairy tale where a beautiful daughter of a merchant boldly takes her father’s place after he steals from an angry beast.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

578320.title: The Outlaws
578320.description: The movie tells a story of a fearless detective Ma Seok-do who hunts down Jang Chen, a cold-blooded boss of Heuksapa, an uprising crial organization that turned Seoul’s Chinatown into a blood bath. Ma Seok-do is an old school detective with bravado who has been protecting the peace of his city with his strong fists and bold spirit. Together with Jeon Il-man, Seok-do plans an ultimate crime sweep to take down Jang Chen’s gangs in one night.

581872.title: The King's Avatar: For the Glory (Dubbed)
581872.description: After being selected to compete in an elite electronic sports championship, a squad of young gamers prepares for the epic showdown.

585784.title: Chronicles of the Ghostly Tribe
585784.description: A famous professor and his research team discover massive fossils of unknown origin in the mountains of the Mongolian Border before monsters attack.

585846.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil
585846.description: A crime boss with retribution on his mind after surviving a near-fatal attack by a serial killer convinces a detective to help catch the murderer.

589980.title: Kill Zone 2 (Español)
589980.description: Después de que se revela que es policía, un hombre termina en una prisión donde debe evitar que un alcaide corrupto y un criminal extraigan órganos.

589987.title: Train to Busan (Español)
589987.description: A train trip from Seoul to Busan becomes the ultimate hell ride when a zombie plague breaks out amongst the passengers. Who will survive?

590016.title: Iceman
590016.description: A wild prehistoric tale, set in the Otztal Alps over 5,000 years ago, unfolds, as a Neolithic man whose settlement is attacked lives his final days.

590183.title: The First King (English Dub)
590183.description: The story of shepard brothers Romulus and Remus, who find their tight bond turning into something entirely different when it comes to who will rule.

590392.title: Memories
590392.description: The anime anthology classic from the creator of “Akira” featuring three visually incredible stories from the top animation studios in Japan.

590740.title: The Man From Nowhere (English Dubbed)
590740.description: An ex-enforcer sets aside his new and quietly humble life to take on a brutal trafficking ring to keep a child, his only friend, from harm’s way.

599086.title: The Third Wife
599086.description: After becoming the third wife to a wealthy landowner in 19th century Vietnam, May struggles with family and the prospects of motherhood.

600075.title: Run Boy Run
600075.description: A superlative saga of courage and compassion, Run Boy Run tells the extraordinary true story of a young Polish boy’s struggle to outlast the Nazi occupation and maintain his Jewish faith through his intrepid will and the kindness of others. Escaping the Warsaw ghetto at the behest of his father, nine-year old Srulik (movingly portrayed by twins Andrzej and Kamil Tkacz) flees to the woods. There, he learns to hide from SS patrols and scour for food, until loneliness and the harsh onset of winter drive him back to civilization. An unforgettable cinematic experience featuring exceptional performances, arresting cinematography and a transcendent musical score, Run Boy Run is directed by Oscar-winner Pepe Danquart and based on the bestselling novel by Israeli author Uri Orlev.

601870.title: The Beautiful Troublemaker
601870.description: A once-famous painter restarts an abandoned project and stirs up issues of the creative process and its limits when he chooses a new female muse.

605440.title: 4some
605440.description: Two couples who have been mutual friends for decades make the switch to polyamory amongst themselves and have to explain it to their families.

605620.title: Bedways
605620.description: When a filmmaker invites her friends to act in a film about modern love and sexuality, their relationships are pushed into uncharted erotic territory.

605625.title: The Slut
605625.description: A vibrant, beautiful mother enjoys meaningless sexual trysts, until a young veterinarian falls under her spell and challenges her polyamorous ways.

605688.title: Obsessed
605688.description: A Colonel with PTSD returns from Vietnam in the summer of 1969 and strays from his loveless marriage when he falls for a neighboring military wife.

606360.title: Desire (Subbed)
606360.description: Twenty-year-old Cecile copes with the grief of her father’s recent death by having sex with strangers whose lives she manages to turn upside-down.

608018.title: Fuerte Solitario (Doblado)
608018.description: En las áridas tierras fronterizas de Texas, hay una oleada de asesinatos y el mayor sospechoso es un joven vagabundo que se acaba de mudar.

608514.title: Asesinada (Doblado)
608514.description: Cathy se estuvo preparando desde temprano para celebrar el cumpleaños de su hija Eva y no se esperaba la desgarradora noticia de que la mataron.

608619.title: Aca y Acullá (Here and Yonder)
608619.description: Los chicos de un colegio armenio en Argentina conmemoran el centenario del genocidio de su pueblo durante un taller de cinematografía.

608643.title: Coria Y El Mar (Subbed)
608643.description: Son mujeres saharauis en campos de refugiados esperanzadas en que las nuevas generaciones vean algún día el mar de su terruño que no conocieron.

608652.title: Chubut, Libertad Y Tierra
608652.description: Una mujer empieza a entender la realidad histórica de la Patagonia siguiendo los rastros de su abuelo en un viaje desde la costa a las cordilleras.

608655.title: La Película Infinita
608655.description: De fragmentos de películas argentinas que nunca llegaron a existir surge una historia paralela del séptimo arte en este ensayo cinematográfico.

608703.title: Las Facultades
608703.description: En las universidades públicas de Argentina, los estudiantes se preparan tratando de apaciguar los nervios para presentar los exámenes orales finales.

609121.title: Pinamar
609121.description: Al regresar a su ciudad a esparcir las cenizas de su madre y vender el apartamento familiar, dos hermanos son acosados por sus recuerdos y deseos.

609123.title: Relámpago en La Oscuridad
609123.description: Get to know the compelling life story of Alberto Zamarbide, Argentina’s first heavy metal singer, as described by other influential musicians.

609204.title: Vigilia
609204.description: A prodigal son returns to his family farm during a biblical drought that has driven the animals mad and wiped out their Northern Argentina town.

609206.title: Ínsula
609206.description: A pair of documentary filmmakers working on a piece about the aboriginal community of El Traslado disagree about the direction of their project.

609668.title: Untold Scandal
609668.description: Palace intrigue threatens to take down the innocent victims of a ruthless personal bet that a royal woman makes with an equally narcissistic playboy.

609894.title: La Venganza De Los Cheyenes (Doblado)
609894.description: Cuando unos apaches secuestran a una joven pionera, su hermano se propone rescartarla y, para hallarla, pide ayuda a un prospector amigo de la bebida.

610449.title: Infierno Grande
610449.description: A pregnant teacher from a small Argentinian town reaches her breaking point with her violent husband and runs away from home and heads to the desert.

610454.title: The Wolf House
610454.description: After narrowly escaping with her life from a sect of German religious fanatics, a young woman finds uncertain refuge in a strange house in the woods.

612737.title: The Tunnel
612737.description: Christmas commuters get trapped and desperate when they are stuck in a tunnel with an exploded truck and a blizzard that’s blocking first responders.

613784.title: Hercules Y La Conquista De La Atlantida
613784.description: La reina de la Atlántida conspira para apoderarse del mundo y, cuando el rey de Tebas es secuestrado, su fiel compañero Hércules sale al rescate.

614117.title: Innocent Thing
614117.description: An innocent high school girl’s crush on her popular gym teacher becomes a mad obsession that threatens his marriage, career, and everything he values.

615626.title: Más Valientes Que Los Hombres (Doblado)
615626.description: La aventura y drama de siete niños que pierden sus padres al cruzar el pais en un vagon con la esperanza de una vida mejor en el territorio de Oregon.

615627.title: El Ángel Y El Pistolero (Doblado)
615627.description: Quirt Evans, un chico malo en todos los aspectos, conoce a Penélope, una chica cuáquera y debe elegir entre su mundo y el mundo en el que vive ella.

615656.title: Esther Y El Rey (Doblado)
615656.description: Esther (una judía) llama la atención del rey Asuero, que acaba de enviudar y esta tratando de sofocar y derrotar la campaña de odio contra los judíos.

615657.title: El Chico De La Burbuja De Plástico (Doblado)
615657.description: El amor por su vecina hace que un adolescente nacido con deficiencias inmunitarias quiera salir de su burbuja libre de gérmenes.

615658.title: Ahora Empiezan Los Gritos (Doblado)
615658.description: Una joven es víctima de una vieja maldición sobre la familia y en su noche de bodas es violada por un fantasma y queda embarazada.

615659.title: Acoso Mortal Clan Diabolico (Doblado)
615659.description: Cinco niños que se sufren un accidente de bus, comienzan a matar a las personas que los insultaron o fueron groseros con ellos en el albergue.

616433.title: Toda Clase De Extraños
616433.description: Un fotógrafo que viaja por una zona apartada y una mujer son retenidos por un grupo de huérfanos que quieren que se conviertan en sus padres. Desafortunadamente, los niños tienen la costumbre de matar a los adultos que rechazan ese honor en particular.

619748.title: A Breath Away
619748.description: When a deadly fog engulfs Paris, a pair of concerned parents risk everything to find their daughter, who is trapped in a medical tank.

625513.title: Jab We Met
625513.description: A suicidal industrial worker sees his life completely change when he meets a free-spirited and talkative young woman on the train who bonds with him.

628368.title: Adonis
628368.description: A young man, who performs in the Beijing Opera, decides to pursue acting and soon becomes a commercial sex worker for men, in this philosophical film.

631012.title: El Último Día (Doblado)
631012.description: Una tormenta apocalíptica amenaza con arrasar todo un país. Se levanta un estado de emergencia mientras estalla el caos.

641063.title: An Unknown Compelling Force
641063.description: This documentary investigates the 1959 case of nine Russian hikers who died under mysterious circumstances, fueling conspiracy theories.

641665.title: El Miedo No Anda en Burro
641665.description: La India María hereda una fortuna de su patrón que falleció. Los parientes del finado recurrirán a una serie de planes para recuperar la fortuna.

642740.title: T-34 (English Dub)
642740.description: A young Soviet lieutenant tasked with leading a defensive maneuver against the 1944 Nazi invasion has just one beat up T-34 tank at his disposal.

643938.title: Sor Tequila
643938.description: La India María, que es requetebuena para los deportes, se mete de monja y siempre anda metiendo la pata por querer ayudar a la gente.

651585.title: Porn Theatre
651585.description: Award-winning French indie film about the complex love triangle that occurs within an adult film theater frequented by lonely men and prostitutes.

652570.title: Sentiment of the Flesh
652570.description: This intense psycho-sexual thriller takes viewers into the depths of eroticism and surrealism as two medical students get lost in their obsessions.

652742.title: The Concubine (Subbed)
652742.description: Palace intrigue and life-threatening consequences face a royal concubine, her lower class lover and a prince all caught up in a love triangle.

654200.title: En El Pozo
654200.description: When a young woman brings her new boyfriend home and introduces him to old friends, tensions build into gender violence and spiral towards murder.

655373.title: The Pilot
655373.description: A Russian WWII pilot crash-lands in enemy territory and battles hunger, extreme cold and wild animals while evading the Nazis. Based on a true story.

659164.title: The Sister of Ursula
659164.description: Two beautiful sisters in search of their mother check into a posh resort by the sea, just as a mysterious killer starts murdering promiscuous women.

660973.title: Perfume De Violetas
660973.description: Dos adolescentes viviendo en la Ciudad de México entablan una profunda amistad hasta que una de ellas es victima de asalto sexual.

660974.title: Macho
660974.description: Para el mundo, Evaristo Jiménez es un reconocido diseñador de moda femenina, pero no todo en su vida es lo que parece en la superficie.

661040.title: Sexomáticos
661040.description: Lucrecia y Gerardo, un matrimonio feliz, verá interumpida esta tranquilidad cuando el comienza a consultar un sitio en internet llamado Sexomático.

662183.title: Sexo, Amor Y Otras Perversiones
662183.description: Ocho relatos independientes a cargo de prestigiados directores de cine que plasman su visión acerca de las relaciones humanas, el amor y el sexo.

670220.title: La Ley De La Fuerza (Doblado)
670220.description: Una colonia cuáquera intenta salvar a las secuoyas gigantes de un barón maderero que intenta cortarlas para hacer de ellas negocio.

673374.title: Midnight
673374.description: After bearing witness to a murder at the hands of a serial killer, a deaf woman is ruthlessly hunted down by him through the streets of South Korea.

675529.title: 4 Maras
675529.description: Cinco integrantes de una de las tantas Maras, deciden abandonar la ciudad por la persecución en su contra, pero su líder es arrestado.

675531.title: Decadencia
675531.description: Anabel, una hermosa joven colombiana, trabaja como anfitriona, conoce a Oscar, se enamora y comienza a caer en los juegos sexuales de su pareja.

675537.title: Una Fichera Torera
675537.description: Viola, una mujer de cuerpo escultural, trabaja en un burdel desde muy joven y un día, en el burdel, el amor de un hombre la sorprenderá.

676262.title: The Treacherous
676262.description: The Joseon Dynasty, 1504. Upon the tyrannical king’s order, a father and son are dispatched all over the country to find women to entertain him.

676949.title: Serpiente (Doblado)
676949.description: Un grupo de expertos descubren una serpiente mutada en lo profundo de la jungla y se dan cuenta de que pueden no ser rival para este peligroso reptil.

681408.title: El Espectro (Sub Esp)
681408.description: Una mujer y su amante asesinan a su marido. Pronto, sin embargo, empiezan a ocurrir cosas extrañas, y se preguntan si realmente lo mataron.

681500.title: Fashion Bikini Week
681500.description: Follow a group of female contestants from around the world as they all compete to win a fashion bikini contest on the beautiful beaches of Costa Rica.

688622.title: Hercules Encadenado (Doblado)
688622.description: Mientras negocia la paz entre dos hermanos que disputan el trono de Tebas, un Hercules amnesico es seducido por la malvada reina Omphale.

688623.title: Identikit La Masoquista (Doblado)
688623.description: La solterona mentalmente perturbada Lise experimenta una serie de extraños encuentros en Roma mientras busca a alguien que la asesine.

690246.title: Swingers (Sub Esp)
690246.description: A pesar de la naturaleza insegura de Diana, ella y su marido Julián están de acuerdo con la idea de experimentar sexualmente con otra pareja.

693508.title: Buddha Palm
693508.description: To raise money to save his sick little sister, Long Jianbei decides to participate in a human body experiment, giving him superhuman abilities.

693738.title: Snow Monster vs Ice Shark
693738.description: A gene research company sends a group into a mysterious snowy area on the edge of the Arctic where they get attacked by unknown giant creatures.

694833.title: Better Days
694833.description: A relentlessly bullied teen gets dragged into the middle of a murder investigation with a small-time criminal that will change their lives forever.

694888.title: Iron Protector
694888.description: A martial arts master and successor of an ancient Chinese clan must unleash his secret fighting techniques as the bodyguard of a spoiled rich girl.

698786.title: Red Water
698786.description: Four friends who find themselves stranded in a small boat and circled by a blood-thirsty shark must devise a plan to survive or become its next meal.

699188.title: El Tatuaje
699188.description: Esta pelicula es la historia de Sebastián y Valentina, quienes a prueba de amor se tatuaron cada uno en la ingle el nombre del otro.

699192.title: La Seductora
699192.description: Cansada de una vida aburrida y de un hombre incapaz de seguirla y satisfacerla como mujer, Lucy cae rendida ante los encantos de un joven.

699306.title: Salvaje (Doblado)
699306.description: Después de que su camión se avería, cuatro mujeres se encuentran varadas en una gasolinera y se dan cuenta de que es una trampa mortal.

699309.title: The Servant
699309.description: A geisha tries to seduce a powerful nobleman in order to improve her social status, but winds up falling for his servant as well.

700759.title: Alice
700759.description: After her husband's addiction to escorts has left their family penniless, Alice is forced into the world of high-end sex work to support her child.

701801.title: A Werewolf Boy (Subbed)
701801.description: Summoned by an unexpected phone call, a woman visits the cottage she used to live in as a child and recalls the memory of a boy she knew 47 years ago.

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702536.title: Entre Compadres Te Veas
702536.description: Un padre y sus dos hijos deciden divertirse en el primer aniversario de la muerte de su esposa y madre y buscan aventuras en las ferias.

702538.title: Por Tu Maldito Amor
702538.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un ganadero pelea con el actual esposo de su antiguo amor y una machorra y el dueño de una plantación lo ayudan.

702540.title: El Día Del Compadre
702540.description: El día del compadre, los habitantes de un condominio se preparan para festejar y tienen un baile donde suceden varias cosas provocadas por el alcohol.

702542.title: Emboscada
702542.description: Dos hombres sospechan de un presidente y le tienden una trampa para desenmascararlo ante el pueblo sin sospechar que descubrirán otras verdades.

702544.title: En Peligro De Muerte
702544.description: Una reportera en un país latinoamericano en guerra, queda atrapada en la línea de fuego y contrata a un piloto mercenario para que la ayude a salir.

702666.title: El Pequeño Soldado (Doblado)
702666.description: Esta película está basada en la historia real de Seryozha Aleshkov, un niño de seis años, el héroe más joven de Rusia en la Segunda Guerra Mundial.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
